{"tid":891550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女性員工沐浴時闖入 某國國家電台分台長遭解任","createTime":"2018-11-06T08:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T12:15:09.000Z","uid":82640,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa0647416228a7a24616920540edcd152fa6e76f","tid":891550,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"NHK（日本廣播協會）已於5日宣布人事調動，針對現年59歲的佐賀廣電分台台長湧川高史，以其做出「違反職員服務規定的不當行為」為由，自同日起解除台長職務，調至人事局附屬（等待後續調動的身分）。並表示，湧川已遭處以暫停出勤14天的懲戒處分。<br />\n<br />\n湧川曾在前會長籾井勝人的任期間擔任秘書室長。NHK廣報局（公關局）發言：「做出不符合地方分台台長應有的行為，對此事感到極為遺憾。」並表示由於關係到個人隱私，無法回答詳細內容。<br />\n<br />\n根據NHK相關人士指出，湧川日前在其走訪的設施內，闖入NHK女性員工沐浴中的浴室。研判當時湧川已處於酒醉狀態。<br />\n<br />\n酒醉三分醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分台長好識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ebf59a8ff4186e047ae788c1e7ed63a6c94ef8","tid":891550,"uid":1557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T08:49:08.000Z","msg":"日本，中！"},{"pid":"1654e809d0530b8dc5830b5612bd0ca2089bfb3c","tid":891550,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38ebf59a8ff4186e047ae788c1e7ed63a6c94ef8","tid":891550,"uid":1557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T08:49:08.000Z","msg":"日本，中！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"係真唔係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c1ee023c1f30caac11ee72cd3f435108237856","tid":891550,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"有無邊套AV有呢個情節？"},{"pid":"b5611b6df588848e2eda2e516513c6ae0b848195","tid":891550,"uid":64345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:23:19.000Z","msg":"湧川已遭處以暫停出勤14天的懲戒處分。<br />\n<br />\n唔使返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a03c8a947b577ad6626b49b8264eccf45a22a47","tid":891550,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T1